s, debug artifacts, or missing files\n4. If anything fails: one retry via Gemini, then do it yourself\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e0ffd8c9-bab8-4586-8638-f9b34140f056","uuid":"ba588223-c46b-4e1f-a4aa-a37f5fcb9d30","isSynthetic":true}
